        },
        "template--17171074941143__09bcd935-5b4e-4d0b-bd81-3244ec4d6f1c-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><\/p><h5><strong>Eligibility<\/strong><\/h5><p><strong>Open to all registered Mr. Chow customers who are of legal drinking age.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Customers must have a valid Mr. Chow account.<\/strong><\/p><h5><strong>Campaign Period<\/strong><\/h5><p><strong>The campaign starts on 3rd October 2023.<\/strong><\/p><h5><strong>Referral Process<\/strong><\/h5><p><strong>To refer a friend, customers must log in to their account and find their unique referral code in their account dashboard.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Referred friends must make a purchase using the unique referral code to qualify.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Referral codes are valid only during the campaign period.<\/strong><\/p><h5><strong>Discount Mechanism<\/strong><\/h5><p><strong>Customers are able to refer as many friends as they want.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>The referred friend can get RM25 off their purchase with a minimum purchase of RM300.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>As for the customer, when a referred friend makes a purchase, the customer will receive a discount code for the referral.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Tier 1:<br\/>For the first 2 referrals that successfully make a purchase, the customer will receive a 3% discount promo code with no minimum purchase requirement, capped at RM200.<br\/><br\/>Tier 2:<br\/>For the 3rd and 4th referrals that successfully make a purchase, the customer will receive a 4% discount promo code with no minimum purchase requirement, capped at RM200.<br\/><br\/>Tier 3:<br\/>For the 5th referral onwards that successfully make a purchase, the customer will receive a 5% discount promo code with no minimum purchase requirement, capped at RM200.<\/strong><\/p><h5><strong>Discount Redemption<\/strong><\/h5><p><strong>Discounts earned through referrals will be automatically applied to the customer’s next eligible purchase.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Discounts cannot be redeemed for cash or transferred to other accounts.<\/strong><\/p><h5><strong>Validity Period<\/strong><\/h5><p><strong>The discount vouchers earned through referrals will only be valid for 100 days upon receiving the email containing the voucher code.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>By participating in this campaign, customers agree to abide by these Terms and Conditions.<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
